                  , did steal on the <rs id="t18221023-7-cd32" type="crimeDate">17th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18221023-7-off30 t18221023-7-cd32"></join>, three gowns, value 30 s.; six caps, value 48 s., and one pelisse, value 20 s., his property, in the dwelling-house of 
                     <persName id="t18221023-7-person137">
                        William 
                        Odell
                     <interp inst="t18221023-7-person137" type="surname" value="Odell"></interp>
